name: Revi on IRC
body:
### Welcome to Revi's IRC informations.

Please go to [ReviWiki](http://revi.pe.kr/wiki/) for more information, and try to ping Revi on [Freenode](https://freenode.net), [LizardNet](https://lizardirc.org) and some other networks for more informations.
